snippet.title: Match Highlights - Argentina 2:1 Australia - FIFA World Cup Qatar 2022 | JioCinema & Sports18
snippet.description:
Argentina booked their place in the last eight for the 10th time in #FIFAWorldCup history, edging Australia 2-1 at the Ahmad bin Ali Stadium.

Lionel Messi, who hadn't scored in the knockout stages of the competition, opened the scoring in the 35th minute. Julian Alvarez doubled the lead for Lionel Scaloni's side after making the most of an error by Socceroos goalkeeper Mathew Ryan.

Australia pulled one back through an unfortunate own goal by Enzo Fernandez. But Argentina held their nerve to make it through.

Watch Messi & Co. next in action against #Netherlands in the quarter-final on Dec 9 - 8:30 pm, LIVE on #JioCinema & #Sports18 📺📲

#Qatar2022 #WorldsGreatestShow #FIFAWConJioCinema #FIFAWConSports18 #ShortsFIFAWorldCup

Watch FIFA World Cup 2022 live on JioCinema! 
Download Now: https://bit.ly/3AWBqZf

snippet.title: Filmymoji || Middle Class Madhu || Saradaaga || A Family Picnic || MCM
snippet.description:
Filmymoji || Middle Class Madhu || Saradaaga || A Family Picnic || MCM

In this new saradaga episode of Middle Class Madhu, a funny discussion starts between 1A Master and his wife Bhagyam. The discussion later turns into a serious plan when Bhagyam asks him to plan a picnic with the colony. She motivates 1A Master to be the mastermind behind the picnic plan while they portray the plan being executed by Sarada Subbarao. Finally, after convincing sarada Subba Rao, the picnic plan gets started. In surprise, Budatha invites his girlfriend Geetha to the picnic. Seeing Geetha madhu surprises him and he tries to put a fight between Geetha and Budatha, but his plan turns out to be profitable for Budatha. Everybody enjoys the places in Vizag, and Madhu, with his Naatu Guntala Gang, starts funny plans to make the picnic even more funnier. 1A master who is so excited and looking happy in the picnic was the target for Madhu and His Gang. Watch out for this fun-filled episode, Saradaga! And we promise you a 30-minute fun ride.

snippet.title: 🥰 Vaishali ku Naanga kodutha Surprise || Doctor Vaishali is Back 😍|| Oru Long Drive Polama Makkale 🤪
snippet.description:
Hey guys! Welcome to our channel! So what's the best way to celebrate comebacks? Sometime back, Vaishali returned home as a doctor. Living away from home for years and coming back called for a grand welcome.  

This vlog is unique as I welcome Vaishali home with a special gift, a Tata Tigor car, waiting to surprise her! It's a complete joy to see her home, and this moment gets more joyful with the brand-new Tata Tigor. There's no better way than gifting my lady luck a brand-new car and making her feel butterflies all over again!
  
Tata Tigor is India's fasted Sedan, a sub-compact, stylish, and when it hits the road, the world stops and stares! Join us to make this moment of our life worthwhile with love and blessings as we bring this special gift home!
Know more: https://cars.tatamotors.com/cars/tigor

His soul rules his heart and is never without it. Anywhere he goes, his soul shows him the light. Here is the deepest secret nobody knows yet. snippet.title: Mystery of Ancient Pyramids | How were they really built? | Dhruv Rathee
snippet.description:
You must have seen several pictures of Egyptian Pyramids. We all agree that they are really beautiful - but have you ever thought about who built them, and how were they built? Because they were built at a time when there was no machinery, no infrastructure, no technology, nothing. So what is the story behind these giant structures that weigh 6 million tons? Why are they shaped like that? How were the stones transported? Watch this video by Dhruv Rathee to find out as he deep dives into the mystery of Giza Pyramids.

Night Stay at Friend house , her Mom feeding ou Favourite Idli Sambhar , Rajma Chawal , Aunty loves her cooking skills and praises for that . My Culinary journey as a trainee to become an Executive Chef is incredible. My experience in the culinary field is for more than fifteen years and my USP is Indian cooking !! Apart from being a TV cookery host, my experience lies mainly with being employed in some of the major star hotels across the country especially the Marriott group.

     Chef Deena Cooks is my English Youtube Channel! Practical, simple recipes are my forte and using minimal easily available ingredients is my hallmark. snippet.title: EXCLUSIVE : Apoorva Sangama - Anant Nag & Diganth | Thimmayya & Thimmayya | Anushree Anchor
snippet.description:
Anushree Anchor presents my most-awaited interview with the "Thimayya & Thimayya" team. 

It was great sharing space and time with the incredible "Thimayya & Thimayya" team and learning about them. The movie is directed by Sanjay Sharma and features Sandalwood stars Anant Nag, Diganth Manchale, and Aindrita Ray in the lead roles. 

Watch the exclusive interview with "Thimayya & Thimayya" and learn more about the making of this Kannada movie.

snippet.title: Hit 2 Non Spoiler Review | Adivi Sesh, Meenakshi | Sailesh Kolanu, Nani | Telugu Movies | Thyview
snippet.description:
Hello All Welcome to thyview. here is our non-spoiler review of the film Hit 2 directed by DR sailesh Kolanu.

First things first cinema choosaka naa experience cheppali ante, its engaging.decent. baane vundi.2 hours run time helped..but but but meeru usually ilanti thrillers choodaka pothe kanuka meeku khacchitham ga nacchuthundi. ala kakunda meeru naa laaga eppativo criminal minds,Mentalist, ncis, csi, castle nundi monna vacchina mind hunter, mare of eastown, Dahmer documentary daaka ilanti content consume chesunte kanuka meeda ok baane vundi and pedda thrilling ga anipinchaka poina movie end ayinappudu oka satisfaction tho theatre nundi bayataki vastharu.and meelo kontha mandhiki vunde regular questions, Hit 1 kanna bavunda ? i would say yes, this is better written ela anedi detailed ga tharuvatha cheptha.  and next question vacchesi hit2 choodali ante mundu hit1 choodala ? well choosthe konni connections artham avuthai, but choodakapoina hit2 works as a stand alone film.

#Hit2 #adivisesh #SaileshKolanu #Nani #WallPosterCinema #Hit #Meenakshi #MovieReviews #tollywoodMovies #RaoRamesh #Hit3

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Siyani Episode 110 - [Eng Sub] - Anmol Baloch - Mohsin Abbas Haider - Saniya Shamshad - 3rd December 2022

Hailing from a lower-middle-class family, Kiran is a selfish and arrogant girl who aspires to achieve a lifestyle through mending her ways and taking shortcuts. Kiran’s mother Nusrat Ara is aware of her daughter’s nature and doesn’t stop her from doing anything. On the contrary, Ujala is a well-mannered and beautiful girl who lives with Kiran’s family and strives to become independent. 

Zarbab, a handsome young man who belongs to an influential and wealthy family. His first meeting with Kiran turns out to be magical as he falls in love at first sight. Kiran sees him as a way to advance forward in life and builds a web of lies and deceit around Zarbab. On the other hand, Ujala is forced to live a life deprived of love and unfulfilled dreams.

Will Ujala ever find the love and respect that she deserves? After building her life on lies and deception, how long will Kiran be able to conceal the truth?

Written By: Sadia Akhtar
Directed By: Ali Akbar
Produced By: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Zarbab, a handsome young man who belongs to an influential and wealthy family. His first meeting with Kiran turns out to be magical as he falls in love at first sight. Kiran sees him as a way to advance forward in life and builds a web of lies and deceit around Zarbab. On the other hand, Ujala is forced to live a life deprived of love and unfulfilled dreams.

Will Ujala ever find the love and respect that she deserves? After building her life on lies and deception, how long will Kiran be able to conceal the truth?

Dum dum damke jhumka mera, maarda lashkaara,

Rang birangi odhni main, odh aayi yaara,

Sun zara bole kya dil ka iktara..

Resham ka.. haan
Resham ka roomal gale mein daal ke,  tu aaja na.. aa wait karoon main, 

Main cherry wali lipistick lagake, arey.. kab se khadi hoon darwajje pe..

Resham ka.... haan

Meri nathani haale dole, mera bichhua chham bole, Re ,

Meri nathani haale dole, mera bichhua chham chham bole..

Meri laal chunariya, sar se sarakati jaaye

Dildaar mere main, haan branded wala perfume lagaake are, kab se chhupi hoon mai rajaayi mein, o o

Resham ka.. Haan

Jab jab dekhoon chehra tera,
Hosh huye aawaara
Bajaran teri huyi main,
Tu mera banjaara,

Dholna  sabse tu mujhko hai pyaara,

Resham ka...
Resham ka roomal gale mein daalke tu aa jaana, darling mere main,. Main mehngi waali goggle lagake yaham  kab se khadi hoon darwajje pe..oo

Resham ka...

Mai cherry wali lipistick lagake are
Mai mehengi wali goggle lagake aha
Han branded wala perfume lagake  

Kabse khadi hun darawajje pe,o o o
Resham Ka.. Haa

snippet.title: Lakehouse Vlog in Tamil | ஏரிக்கரை வீடு | BBQ Vlog in Tamil
snippet.description:
In this video, join me as I visit a lakehouse and we had a BBQ night and the house had wonderful views of the lake. Alandra also had fun roasting marshmallows. We also visited the state capital and visited a old train museum. The lakeshore was full of shells and we picked a lot of shells for future craft projects. Alandra had a lot of fun with the BBQ. We barbequed some mushrooms, corn, onions peppers, fish and prawns. BBQ was perfect for the cold night.
#bbqnight #travelvlog #steffiulagam 

Friends, hope you liked this week's vlog. See you next week with more interesting videos.

snippet.title: Jetha ने खाए Daya के हाथ के मज़ेदार पकवान | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | FE 1389 | 29 Nov 2022
snippet.description:
Episode 1389: Jetha ने खाए Daya के हाथ के मज़ेदार पकवान 
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
Even after meeting Big B in real life, Gokuldham residents cannot believe that they have witnessed such a historic moment in their lives. Everyone is replaying the moments again and again in their minds and trying to bask in the glory of meeting Amitabh Bachchan in real life. The Gada family is no different with Daya calling her family and telling them all about it. Jetha is enjoying the tasty dishes prepared by Daya.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 1389
Produced By -  Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा  #sonypal 

Subscribe to Sony Pal: http:/a/www.youtube.com/sonypalindia

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. Even after meeting Big B in real life, Gokuldham residents cannot believe that they have witnessed such a historic moment in their lives. About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.title: Armaan Malik - Sun Maahi (Official Music Video) | Amaal Mallik, Kunaal Vermaa | Always Music Global
snippet.description:
'Sun Maahi' talks about the ethereal feeling of being completely lost in the magical world of this one's love and creating a universe of their own. It's not limited to your romantic partners but for anyone who you would go to the moon and back. The lyrics written by Kunaal will take you on the ride of exploring the enchanting journey of failing to know how and why you love someone backed with Amaal's fervent composition that gives my vocals a perfect canvas to articulate my emotions. I sincerely hope that my fans experience 'Sun Maahi' and get transported into their own world of unexplained, beautiful, and surreal love-stories.

snippet.description:

Presenting Vicky Kaushal and Kiara Advani in a never-before-seen avatar, “Bana Sharabi” from Govinda Naam Mera is composed and written by Tanishk Bagchi. Sung by Jubin Nautiyal, we recommend you listen to it on your earphones for the complete magical experience!

snippet.title: WOH – Ikka x Dino James x Badshah (Official Lyric Video) | Def Jam India
snippet.description:
India’s Hip-Hop superstars Ikka, Dino James & Badshah come together to channel their inner hopeless romanticism on ‘Woh.’ The track captures the immense hurt, emotions and male vulnerability which comes at the backdrop of a heartbreak. ‘Woh’ is one of the very few records which portray a man’s emotions with evocative honesty and reveals the softer side of him. Dino James pens down the difficulties behind missing someone that he has loved. He feels helpless and apologetic. Ikka feels his heart sinking as he is incapable of fixing the broken relationship and cannot deal with the heartache anymore. Badshah’s verse starts by asserting that it is okay for a man to break down and go through the gut-wrenching feeling of a fleeting romance. ‘Woh’ is an extremely personal track which is bound to shake you if you have ever loved someone.

Stream Now on Spotify: https://open.spotify.com/track/1QUU43rTDMnGl4xyaIfsYN?si=42981c97ba014563

snippet.title: NEW! Maddam Sir - Ep 674 - 2 Dec 2022 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 674: Aakhri Ladai
--------------------------------------------
Shivani has taken it upon herself to take some extreme steps when she points a gun at Karishma Singh. Tai stands in between the gun and Karishma Singh. She even tries to make Shivani understand but Shivani is beyond understanding. Police have infiltrated the gang's place and they reach the place just in time. Chaos breaks out and during the shuffle, Shivani by mistake fires the gun and Tai is the target by chance. After Tai is no more, Shivani understands her mistakes and accepts her own mistakes. She takes all of the responsibility of the dealings of the Chingari Gang, and she decides to surrender herself.
 
Show Name – Maddam Sir
Star Cast –  Gulki Joshi, Yukti Kapoor, Sonali Naik, Bhavika Sharma, Pankhuri Awasthy Rode, Priyanshu Singh, and Ajay Jadhav
Episode No – 674, 2 Dec 2022
Produced By –  Jay Mehta

#MaddamSir  #मैड्डमसर #SAB

Click here to Subscribe to SAB TV Channel: 
https://www.youtube.com/user/sabtv?sub_confirmation=1

About The Show:
-----------------------------
Set in Lucknow the show is based in one such all-women Police station made by 4 beautiful quirky women. Pushpa, the oldest of them, is the head constable who tries to balance her life between home and work. Karishma, the Sub Inspector, is fish out of the water as she is at loggerheads with the philosophy of the police station. She beats before she talks but now she has to solve all cases through reconciliation. Santosh Sharma is a young new recruit and a typical lonely girl in the city. The head of the pack is S.H.O Haseena Mallik, witty, romantic leads by example. The common challenge for all these women is to bring sensitivity to their policing while dealing with cases that come to this police station. Hence their solution is most unusual. The characters and the cases add to the fun and humor of the show. While Pushpa and Karishma are the saas-bahu duo, who keep us entertained by their Squabbles, Haseena - Karishma's ideological differences add to the drama madam and comedy.
